SUBCONTRACT AGREEMENT
Plumbing Works
Agreement Date: 5 July 2024
Project: New Dwelling - 123 Sunset Boulevard, Sydney NSW
Principal Contractor:
ABC Construction Pty Ltd | ABN: 12 345 678 901 | License: 123456C
Subcontractor:
John's Plumbing Services Pty Ltd | ABN: 55 667 889 001 | License: PL-234567
WORKS TO BE PERFORMED:
Complete plumbing installation including:
(cid:127) Cold and hot water supply systems (copper and PEX pipe)
(cid:127) Sanitary drainage (PVC 100mm and 150mm)
(cid:127) Stormwater drainage and connection to Council system
(cid:127) Installation of fixtures: toilets, basins, showers, bath, kitchen sink
(cid:127) Hot water system connection (315L electric storage)
(cid:127) Backflow prevention devices
(cid:127) Pressure testing and certification to AS/NZS 3500
CONTRACT SUM: $19,150.00 (inc GST)
PAYMENT SCHEDULE:
(cid:127) Monthly progress claims based on work completed
(cid:127) Payment within 30 days of approved claim
(cid:127) 5% retention until final completion + 90 d
